flowchart TD
    A([Invoices list]) -->|Click 'Create Invoice'| B{Template saved?}
    B -->|First time| C[Theme modal — pick template]
    B -->|Returning| D[Invoice document opens on dark stage]
    C -->|Start| D

    D --> E[Invoice shown with empty regions]
    E -->|Click any region| F[Floating edit panel anchors to region]

    F -->|Edit Client region| F1[Partner selector — panel updates 'Bill To' live]
    F -->|Edit Items region| F2[Item editor — rows update in doc live]
    F -->|Edit Details region| F3[Date + invoice number + compliance fields]
    F -->|Edit Payment region| F4[Payment toggles + T&C]

    F1 -->|Done| G[Region marked complete in toolbar]
    F2 -->|Done| G
    F3 -->|Done| G
    F4 -->|Done| G

    G -->|Continue editing other regions| F
    G -->|All 4 complete| H{Ready?}
    H -->|Save Draft| I([Invoice saved as Draft])
    H -->|Activate Invoice| J{Partner status?}
    J -->|Activated| K([Invoice Active · navigate to detail])
    J -->|Verifying| L([Draft saved · dialog shown])

    style A fill:#ADB5BD,color:#fff
    style K fill:#6C757D,color:#fff
    style L fill:#6C757D,color:#fff
    style I fill:#6C757D,color:#fff
